                            <comment id="16064459" author="davsclaus" created="Tue, 27 Jun 2017 08:25:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can you try to modify the type converters in camel-mongodb3 / camel-mongodb to not use try .. catch but throw an exception if conversion fails. They should not really do this.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="16066463" author="fabryprog" created="Wed, 28 Jun 2017 13:09:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=davsclaus&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;davsclaus&quot;&gt;davsclaus&lt;/a&gt; now it is work fine.&lt;/p&gt;

